'''Ifaba''' is a monkey that runs the [[Ifaba's General Store|general store]] on [[Ape Atoll]]. His wares are similar to those of other [[general store]]s.

One of the [[monkey greegree]]s and a [[Monkeyspeak amulet]] must be equipped to talk to him, but the amulet is not required to use the shop by using the trade option on him.

This shop can be thieved with at least 5 [[Thieving]], but it is highly risky. Interestingly, the [[tinderbox]] on his [[stall]] is white rather than the usual grey. He does not sell white tinderboxes, however, only the regular grey ones.

